---
/**
 * File: src/components/sections/shared/HowItWorks/index.astro
 * Shared “How our CV writing process works” section.
 * Reused on:
 * - Home page
 * - CV Writing service page
 */

import "./HowItWorks.css";
---

<section class="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="cv-how-it-works">
  <div class="how-it-works__inner">
    <header class="how-it-works__head">
      <h2 id="cv-how-it-works" class="h2 how-it-works__heading">
        How our CV writing process works
      </h2>
      <p class="how-it-works__intro">
        A structured, outcome-focused process designed to reduce uncertainty
        and keep you informed at each stage.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="how-it-works__grid">
      <!-- STEP 1 -->
      <article class="how-it-works__step">
        <p class="how-it-works__step-label">Step 1 · Discovery</p>
        <h3 class="h4 how-it-works__step-title">Clarify your goals</h3>
        <p class="how-it-works__step-body">
          We review your existing CV, understand your target roles, and map
          the positioning needed to present you clearly.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- STEP 2 -->
      <article class="how-it-works__step">
        <p class="how-it-works__step-label">Step 2 · Drafting</p>
        <h3 class="h4 how-it-works__step-title">
          Build a structured, impact-led CV
        </h3>
        <p class="how-it-works__step-body">
          We craft your CV using modern formatting, quantified achievements,
          and recruiter-friendly language aligned to Kenyan expectations.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- STEP 3 -->
      <article class="how-it-works__step">
        <p class="how-it-works__step-label">Step 3 · Review &amp; Revision</p>
        <h3 class="h4 how-it-works__step-title">
          Refine tone, emphasis, and targeting
        </h3>
        <p class="how-it-works__step-body">
          You review the first draft and share your feedback. We refine
          clarity, structure, and messaging so the CV reflects your
          strengths accurately and aligns with your intended career
          direction.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- STEP 4 -->
      <article class="how-it-works__step">
        <p class="how-it-works__step-label">
          Step 4 · Final Polish &amp; Delivery
        </p>
        <h3 class="h4 how-it-works__step-title">
          Prepare a clean, interview-ready version
        </h3>
        <p class="how-it-works__step-body">
          We apply final edits to ensure consistency, precision, and
          ATS-safe formatting. You receive the polished CV in Word and
          PDF—ready for applications and recruiter sharing.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
